latestIgtvVideos.title: Andaman♥️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Basically this place has my ❤️. I strongly suggest everyone to see this place its just literally heaven on earth and every other beautiful thing you can mention or think of. 

Starting from the best of the beaches present here to the great variety of sea life this place fills my heart. And the people the culture tu place is so clean we can barely think of some place like this in India. A true gem and hidden and unexplored place. ♥️
It doesn’t only have oceans but forests and every other geographic landscape you mention of. The only mud valcano present in india is there as well and dont forget the tribals.
Thank you for all the salty memories 😅☺️
